He's got Amélie.

822
01:30:05,875 --> 01:30:08,417
Trust me... he'll give her
back to us.

823
01:30:22,875 --> 01:30:24,500
You know, Franck,

824
01:30:26,333 --> 01:30:29,208
nobody understands
what I'm looking for.

825
01:30:30,542 --> 01:30:32,000
Nobody.

826
01:30:32,958 --> 01:30:34,500
Nobody.

827
01:30:35,917 --> 01:30:37,625
Filthy scum!

828
01:30:39,208 --> 01:30:42,208
It's all over, now.

829
01:30:42,625 --> 01:30:43,875
We're all back together.

830
01:30:44,250 --> 01:30:45,417
The whole family.

831
01:30:45,667 --> 01:30:48,125
Not in front of her.
Drop your gun!

832
01:30:49,000 --> 01:30:49,667
I said

833
01:30:50,083 --> 01:30:51,417
drop your gun!

834
01:30:52,333 --> 01:30:54,125
He's here... I've got him.

835
01:30:56,875 --> 01:30:58,125
He wanted to kill us!

836
01:30:58,542 --> 01:30:59,458
Don't move!

837
01:31:02,958 --> 01:31:04,667
Jean-Louis!

838
01:31:06,708 --> 01:31:07,792
Jean-Louis!

839
01:31:27,542 --> 01:31:30,167
Get him!
he's got Amélie!

840
01:31:32,125 --> 01:31:32,875
The cop?

841
01:31:33,292 --> 01:31:34,708
I'll fix that.

842
01:33:02,500 --> 01:33:03,750
Stop here.

843
01:33:06,167 --> 01:33:08,125
You go on, I'll take a look.

844
01:33:28,583 --> 01:33:31,833
Would you like to walk on ahead, Amélie?

845
01:33:58,917 --> 01:34:01,875
Don't go near the edge.
Stay close to Daddy.

846
01:34:28,167 --> 01:34:30,625
You OK, Franck?

847
01:34:42,333 --> 01:34:43,333
Maurel.

848
01:34:46,125 --> 01:34:47,125
Maurel!

849
01:34:51,500 --> 01:34:53,208
Don't move.
Drop your gun!

850
01:34:55,042 --> 01:34:56,042
I've got the fugitive.

851
01:34:56,458 --> 01:34:58,333
He's down there.

852
01:35:09,917 --> 01:35:10,667
Maurel!

853
01:35:31,292 --> 01:35:32,750
Help's coming.

854
01:35:33,000 --> 01:35:33,750
Franck.

855
01:35:34,125 --> 01:35:36,250
It's all over, Amélie's safe.

856
01:35:39,583 --> 01:35:41,125
Cri de douleur

857
01:35:41,500 --> 01:35:43,042
There's extenuating circumstances.

858
01:35:43,417 --> 01:35:44,417
Trust me.

859
01:35:47,083 --> 01:35:48,167
I can't trust anyone.

860
01:35:48,792 --> 01:35:50,417
It'll be the last time.

861
01:36:00,083 --> 01:36:02,625
Who fired? You bastard!

862
01:36:05,458 --> 01:36:08,708
It came from over there!
Drop it you bastard!

863
01:36:09,000 --> 01:36:11,625
Drop your gun!
Don't move!

864
01:36:11,875 --> 01:36:12,792
Raise your hands.

865
01:36:13,083 --> 01:36:15,125
In the air!
Don't move!

866
01:36:18,958 --> 01:36:20,375
Take it easy.

867
01:37:02,625 --> 01:37:04,250
Look along here.

868
01:37:04,625 --> 01:37:06,167
That's it, thanks.

869
01:37:06,542 --> 01:37:08,500
I'm here.

870
01:37:09,250 --> 01:37:10,667
You OK?
Yes, thanks.

871
01:37:11,042 --> 01:37:12,208
We've got Maurel.

872
01:37:13,333 --> 01:37:16,083
Adrien's body must have gone further.
We'll find it.

873
01:37:20,500 --> 01:37:21,958
You know, Claire...

874
01:37:24,958 --> 01:37:26,500
No better.

875
01:37:31,042 --> 01:37:32,833
Maurel's wife's
spilled the beans.

876
01:37:33,083 --> 01:37:35,292
He was doing all the killing
and raping. Not Adrien.

877
01:37:37,458 --> 01:37:40,000
She's admitted 8 murders,
but there's others.

878
01:37:40,625 --> 01:37:42,500
Without Adrien,
there would have been more.

879
01:37:44,250 --> 01:37:45,167
Go and tell him.

880
01:37:46,958 --> 01:37:48,042
And say what?

881
01:37:48,750 --> 01:37:50,208
I lack your woman's intuition.

882
01:37:53,917 --> 01:37:55,000
Thank you, Claire.

883
01:37:57,000 --> 01:37:59,292
I tried to aim for once

884
01:38:17,000 --> 01:38:19,083
Three months later

885
01:38:38,417 --> 01:38:41,125
She's solitary,
but she's hanging in there.

886
01:38:41,833 --> 01:38:43,000
She's working better

887
01:38:43,375 --> 01:38:44,958
with the speech therapist.

888
01:38:45,208 --> 01:38:46,125
She's happy

889
01:38:46,500 --> 01:38:48,542
when you come to see her.

890
01:38:49,333 --> 01:38:51,792
You told me to tell you
about any mail.

891
01:38:52,917 --> 01:38:53,750
She got a letter.

892
01:38:54,167 --> 01:38:56,042
I have a photocopy.

893
01:38:58,208 --> 01:39:00,250
From Morocco?

894
01:39:05,292 --> 01:39:06,542
Just this, no words?

895
01:39:07,750 --> 01:39:10,208
No, since she got the letter,

896
01:39:10,625 --> 01:39:13,292
she's seemed happier.

897
01:39:14,542 --> 01:39:16,125
Do you know who it's from?

898
01:39:30,542 --> 01:39:31,792
Papa.

899
01:39:49,400 --> 01:39:52,900
